<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA34">
<l>vakaiyā lavaṉi yirantaḷantāy pātam</l>
<l>pukaiyā ṉaṟumalarāṉ muṉṉē – mikavāynta</l>
<l>vaṉpākki yētti yaṭimaippaṭ ṭēṉuṉak</l>
<l>keṉpākki yattā liṉi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Praising the feet of you, who once had begged for and by that way</l>
<l>measured the earth, [and] with incense [and] fragrant blossoms</l>
<l>practicing love that is very exulted, I have fallen in servitude to you now,</l>
<l>by my good fortune.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
